# ACLs for the telemetry system

# Drone publisher can write to telemetry topics only
user drone
topic write drone/telemetry
topic write drone/telemetry/health
topic read  drone/commands/#

# Consumer (cloud processing) can read telemetry and write processed data
user consumer
topic read  drone/telemetry
topic write drone/telemetry/signed
topic write drone/logs/#

# Grafana/Telegraf readers (optional)
user grafana
topic read drone/telemetry/signed
